This code creates the grid structure shown in the image with:
- A vertical column of cells
- An L-shaped arrangement of cells
- The diagonal line connecting points v' and v
- All the appropriate labels (q_t, q_{t*}, q_0, q'_{t'}, and Q_{2r})
- The two points v and v' marked with small filled circles

The scale parameter can be adjusted if you need the diagram to be larger or smaller.

